  "title": "Ender Barrels",
  "description": "Barrels with item teleport skills",
  "body": "Based on [BlockerLocker's Barrelporters commands](https://github.com/blockerlocker/youtube/blob/main/commands/Barrelporters.md). \n\nThis datapack(mod) adds ender barrels to the game which are like little item portals. drop a ender eye and a ender pearl on a barrel they turn into a sender and a receiver barrel. put an item into ender eye barrel and watch it teleporting to the ender pearn barrel. you can point a receiver barrel with multiple sender barrels. also you can rename tha barrels via anvil to link them by name\n\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/t8jcq8QVPzU\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>",
